# Constitution: VReader — Digiteka

## Stack
- Language: Swift 6
- UI Framework: SwiftUI
- Data: SwiftData
- Minimum target: iOS 17.0, iPadOS 17.0
- Mac Catalyst: macOS 14+
- Xcode: 16+
- Supported formats: PDF, EPUB, FB2, FB2.ZIP, CBZ, CBR, CBT, CB7,
  MOBI, AZW3, DJVU, TXT, RTF, CHM, MP3, M4A, M4B, AAC
- Cloud: iCloud Drive, WebDAV, Yandex.Disk, Nextcloud, Mail.ru,
  Google Drive (OAuth2), Dropbox (OAuth2), OneDrive (OAuth2), SMB
- AI: Gemini API (translation, TTS, summaries, X-Ray, dictionary)
- Purchases: StoreKit 2 (iOS 15+)
- Metadata: Google Books API, OpenLibrary API
- Sync: CloudKit (annotations, progress),
  NSUbiquitousKeyValueStore (reading position)
- Storage: Keychain for credentials, SwiftData for library,
  iCloudSettingsStore for settings

## Coding Standards
- No comments in code
- camelCase for variables and functions, PascalCase for types
- All user-facing strings only via L10n.*
- Files published as packages only — dependent files always together
- Mandatory validation via check_refs.py before publishing
- Colors, fonts, spacing only via DesignTokens.swift
- Themes only via @Environment(\.appTheme) — no hardcoded values

## Testing
- check_refs.py mandatory before every merge
- Checks: duplicate types, unresolved references,
  iOS 17+ compatibility, Swift file structural integrity
- Proactive validation only — reactive debugging is forbidden

## Constraints
- iOS 17+ compatibility required everywhere
- UTType for non-standard extensions — optional only,
  force-unwrap forbidden
- NSUbiquitousKeyValueStore requires entitlement —
  do not use without com.apple.developer.ubiquity-kvs-identifier
- CloudKit requires entitlement com.apple.developer.icloud-services
- Credentials only in Keychain
- StoreKit 2 — the only way to handle purchases
- Gemini API key only in Keychain, never in code or UserDefaults
- OAuth only via ASWebAuthenticationSession (never WKWebView)
- Dependent files published together only

## Security
- All passwords, tokens and API keys — only Keychain
  (KeychainManager.shared)
- No credentials in logs, UI state or UserDefaults
- WebDAV Basic Auth only via URLCredential + Keychain
- OAuth tokens (Google, Dropbox, OneDrive) — only Keychain
- secrets.yaml must not be committed to Git
- StoreKit receipt verification on every launch

## LLM Rules
- No stubs without explicit justification
- Always generate AI_NOTES.md for every stage
- Do not duplicate existing types — check first
- Verify all dependencies exist before writing files
- Code language: English
- UI language: RU + EN via L10n (priority), AR + ZH (milestone 09)
